a) A Digital Certificate Issuer component configured to generate digital certificates based on predefined criteria using verifiable credentials;

b) A Digital Wallet component integrated with a blockchain network enabling secure storage of digital certificates;

c) A Permit Application Portal component providing an online interface for authorized users to submit permit requests;

d) A Reviewer Component evaluating submitted permit requests against established criteria and sending notifications to Digital Certificate Issuer component;

e) A Machine Learning Component utilizing advanced algorithms to analyze past permit requests, detect anomalies or fraudulent activities, and suggest improvements continually;

f) A Blockchain Network connecting all components for secure storage and sharing of digital certificates while enabling real-time tracking of permit request statuses;

g) The system further comprising an automated review process leveraging machine learning algorithms to enhance efficiency in the permit application process while maintaining high standards of accuracy and security.

